OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers in the west and the north will
OL,7,Fclear during the evening. Increasing
OL,8,Fclear periods and winds falling light
OL,9,Fovernight bring a patchy inland frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FThe morning will begin dry
OL,12,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Cloud and
OL,13,Fscattered showers spread north from
OL,14,Fthe late morning, heavy at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,17,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday morning.
OL,18,FCloud and rain, heavy at times, spread
OL,19,Fnortheast late Tuesday, clearing later
OL,20,FWednesday. Sunny spells and scattered
OL,21,Fshowers from the west Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
